{"tid":1331919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地盤挖泥機翻側 工人拋出壓死","createTime":"2019-07-19T06:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T06:21:42.000Z","uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9613f6bc8a1856ff240f1cd735c935878ee0e11","tid":1331919,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:18:41.000Z","msg":"地盤挖泥機翻側 工人拋出壓死<br />\n分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190719/large/1563468519_b4fa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563468519_b4fa.gif&h=de30fc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大埔沙欄路地盤的挖泥機翻側，壓斃工人。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔沙欄路近陳屋村一個地盤昨日發生奪命工業意外，一名工人操作挖泥機在斜坡工作期間，疑因泥土鬆軟挖泥機突然失控翻側，工人拋出機外被壓住，經消防救出送院搶救，證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n47歲死者姓張，胸部及腹部受傷，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>妻子及兩子女同住深圳</strong></span></span>。現場為一個村屋地盤，正進行斜坡鞏固工程。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨11時許，張駕挖泥機在斜坡工作期間，疑因泥土鬆軟不平，挖泥機突然之間翻倒，張被拋出機外並遭壓住重傷昏迷，63歲姓朱工友發現報警。警員及消防員到場將張送院搶救，惜已返魂乏術。<br />\n<br />\n去年1月流浮山亦曾發生類似意外，62歲工人在魚塘邊操作挖泥機清理塘內淤泥時，挖泥機失平衡翻跌落魚塘，工人頭部撞傷斃命。<br />\n<br />\n根據勞工處的資料，挖泥機操作員必須接受訓練並持有效證書，僱主安排員工進行有關工序前，須評估操作挖泥機涉及的危險，包括地盤環境的各項因素，如土壤狀況及斜坡傾角。<br />\n■記者劉柏麟"},{"pid":"1125334f33bffb5b43c26d3d4179d3677a4f73da","tid":1331919,"uid":27452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a206e334a1b1303a244c70b8d92385dac576aa","tid":1331919,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGEm7kx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGEm7kx.png&h=84eef868&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VR1gWdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVR1gWdS.png&h=e9b1febb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4w4Y9yT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4w4Y9yT.png&h=5088c22f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有人話我知原來7月20取消左<br />\n<br />\nPrint 出黎痴係連儂牆比老人家知<br />\n<br />\nAirdrop 比人<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞到老人家白行一趟</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}